#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "Labrador mutt"
msgid_plural "Labrador mutts"
msgstr[0] "拉布拉多混种犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Labrador mutt'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"This once-average Labrador mixed breed dog has clearly gone feral.  Though "
"it likely still instinctually trusts humans, it's probably far from domestic"
" by now."
msgstr "这只曾经普通的拉布拉多混种犬显然已变得野性十足。尽管它可能仍本能地信任人类，但如今已远非家养状态。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack labrador"
msgid_plural "attack labradors"
msgstr[0] "攻击型拉布拉多犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack labrador'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A shaggy Labrador Retriever that has been trained to fight.  Improved "
"agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只毛发蓬松的拉布拉多猎犬，经过战斗训练。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、与主人的羁绊以及速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "bulldog"
msgid_plural "bulldogs"
msgstr[0] "斗牛犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bulldog'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The American Bulldog is a hardy, well built dog, that seems suited for "
"surviving the apocalypse.  Can be trained as an attack dog."
msgstr "美国斗牛犬是一种强壮、体格健硕的犬种，似乎很适合在末日中生存。可训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack bulldog"
msgid_plural "attack bulldogs"
msgstr[0] "攻击型斗牛犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack bulldog'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A muscular American Bulldog that has been trained to fight.  Improved "
"agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只肌肉发达的美国斗牛犬，经过战斗训练。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、与主人的羁绊以及速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "cattle dog"
msgid_plural "cattle dogs"
msgstr[0] "牧牛犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cattle dog'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An agile and sturdy breed that is welcome on any farm, the Australian Cattle"
" Dog is adept at leaping fences and herding livestock.  Can be trained as an"
" attack dog."
msgstr "澳大利亚牧牛犬是一种敏捷而强健的品种，在任何农场都受欢迎，擅长跳跃栅栏和驱赶牲畜。可训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack cattle dog"
msgid_plural "attack cattle dogs"
msgstr[0] "攻击型牧牛犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack cattle dog'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A darting Australian Cattle Dog that has been trained to fight.  Improved "
"agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只迅捷的澳大利亚牧牛犬，经过战斗训练。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、与主人的羁绊以及速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "pit bull mix"
msgid_plural "pit bull mixs"
msgstr[0] "比特犬混种"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pit bull mix'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The oft-misunderstood Pit Bull is not actually a single breed but a label "
"for several such as American Pit Bull Terrier and American Staffordshire "
"Terrier.  Average abilities and well-known for their 'lock jaw' which isn't "
"real but their incredible determination is.  Can be trained as an attack "
"dog."
msgstr ""
"常被误解的比特犬并非单一品种，而是对如美国比特斗牛梗和美国斯塔福郡梗等多个品种的统称。能力平均，以“锁颌”闻名（虽非真实），但其惊人的毅力是真实的。可训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack pit bull mix"
msgid_plural "attack pit bull mixs"
msgstr[0] "攻击型比特犬混种"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack pit bull mix'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A ferocious Pit Bull mix that has been trained to fight.  Improved agility, "
"attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只凶猛的比特犬混种，经过战斗训练。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、与主人的羁绊以及速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "beagle"
msgid_plural "beagles"
msgstr[0] "比格犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'beagle'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An adorable Beagle that has managed to survive the apocalypse.  Being agile "
"and small, they are difficult to shoot at.  Generally attacks in packs."
msgstr "一只可爱的比格犬，成功在末日中幸存。因其敏捷和小巧体型，难以被射中。通常成群攻击。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack beagle"
msgid_plural "attack beagles"
msgstr[0] "攻击型比格犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack beagle'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A regal Beagle that has been trained to fight.  Improved agility, attack, "
"health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的威严比格犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "border collie"
msgid_plural "border collies"
msgstr[0] "边境牧羊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'border collie'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An athletic and hyperactive dog that loves to herd animals and jump, the "
"Border Collie is an agile attacker.  Although they can be easy to train, "
"they don't work well in packs.  Can be trained as an attack dog."
msgstr "边境牧羊犬是一种精力充沛、活泼好动的犬种，喜欢驱赶动物和跳跃，是敏捷的攻击者。虽然它们易于训练，但不擅长群体协作。可被训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack border collie"
msgid_plural "attack border collies"
msgstr[0] "攻击型边境牧羊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack border collie'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A hyper Border Collie that has been trained to fight.  Improved agility, "
"attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的亢奋边境牧羊犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "boxer mastiff"
msgid_plural "boxer mastiffs"
msgstr[0] "拳师獒犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boxer mastiff'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"An ordinary breed full of affection, the Boxer Mastiff doesn't stand out "
"amongst other dogs but has mediocre abilities nonetheless.  Can be trained "
"as an attack dog."
msgstr "拳师獒犬是一种充满感情的普通犬种，虽不突出于其他犬类，但能力尚可。可被训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack boxer mastiff"
msgid_plural "attack boxer mastiffs"
msgstr[0] "攻击型拳师獒犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack boxer mastiff'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A stocky Boxer Mastiff that has been trained to fight.  Improved agility, "
"attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的壮实拳师獒犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "chihuahua"
msgid_plural "chihuahuas"
msgstr[0] "吉娃娃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chihuahua'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"It's a tiny Chihuahua.  How it has managed to survive is a miracle; although"
" its small size and aggressive nature may been useful."
msgstr "这是一只小小的吉娃娃。它能存活下来简直是个奇迹；尽管它的小体型和好斗天性或许派上了用场。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack chihuahua"
msgid_plural "attack chihuahuas"
msgstr[0] "攻击型吉娃娃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack chihuahua'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A skittish Chihuahua that has been trained to embrace its bark rather than "
"its bite.  Improved agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过训练、学会发挥吠叫而非撕咬优势的易惊吉娃娃。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "dachshund"
msgid_plural "dachshunds"
msgstr[0] "腊肠犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dachshund'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A weiner dog!  This awkward looking dog can be a useful watch dog, plus it "
"looks adorable as it bumbles around, also making it hard to shoot."
msgstr "一只腊肠犬！这只长相滑稽的狗可以成为有用的看门犬，而且它笨拙地四处走动时看起来很可爱，同时也难以被射中。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack dachshund"
msgid_plural "attack dachshunds"
msgstr[0] "攻击型腊肠犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack dachshund'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A long-bodied Dachshund that has been trained to fight, or so it wants you "
"to believe.  Improved agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的长身腊肠犬，或者说它想让你这么认为。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "german shepherd"
msgid_plural "german shepherds"
msgstr[0] "德国牧羊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'german shepherd'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"The original K-9 breed.  An easy to train and great attack dog that will "
"also defend its owner to the death, however they don't work well in packs.  "
"Can be trained as an attack dog."
msgstr "最初的K-9犬种。一种易于训练的优秀攻击犬，会誓死保卫主人，但它们不擅长群体协作。可被训练为攻击犬。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack german shepherd"
msgid_plural "attack german shepherds"
msgstr[0] "攻击型德国牧羊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack german shepherd'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A noble German Shepherd that has been trained to fight and not flee.  "
"Improved agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练、绝不退缩的高贵德国牧羊犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "great pyrenees"
msgid_plural "great pyreneess"
msgstr[0] "大白熊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'great pyrenees'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A large and powerful breed, the Great Pyrenees has a beautiful, thick white "
"coat.  Originally bred to deter wolves and other predators, now faced with "
"protecting livestock from shambling hordes of undead."
msgstr "大白熊犬是一种大型强壮的犬种，拥有美丽浓密的白色被毛。最初被培育用于威慑狼和其他捕食者，如今则要保护牲畜免受蹒跚而行的亡灵群侵袭。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack great pyrenees"
msgid_plural "attack great pyreneess"
msgstr[0] "攻击型大白熊犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack great pyrenees'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A resilient Great Pyrenees that has been trained to fight.  Improved "
"agility, attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的坚韧大白熊犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "rottweiler"
msgid_plural "rottweilers"
msgstr[0] "罗威纳犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rottweiler'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A terrifying breed to face feral, Rottweilers are descended from Roman "
"legion mastiffs.  It's robust, vicious, and quite capable of mauling a human"
" to death."
msgstr "面对野生的罗威纳犬是一种可怕的经历，它们源自罗马军团獒犬的后代。它强壮、凶猛，完全有能力将人类撕咬致死。"

#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid "attack rottweiler"
msgid_plural "attack rottweilers"
msgstr[0] "攻击型罗威纳犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'attack rottweiler'}
#: .\dog_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A brutal Rottweiler that has been trained to fight.  Improved agility, "
"attack, health, owner bond, and speed."
msgstr "一只经过战斗训练的凶残罗威纳犬。提升了敏捷性、攻击力、生命值、主人羁绊和速度。"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Amateur Dog Trainer"
msgstr "业余训犬师"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Amateur Dog Trainer"
msgstr "业余训犬师"

#. ~ Profession (male Amateur Dog Trainer) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"As a high school student, you were the only member of a canine training "
"club.  You've always been into dogs, but you barely manage to get Fido to "
"sit.  Unfortunately, you'll need to learn quick or you and Fido aren't going"
" to last long in this new world."
msgstr "高中时期，你是犬类训练社的唯一成员。你一直很喜欢狗，但连让菲多坐下都勉强。不幸的是，你必须快速学习，否则你和菲多在这个新世界活不了多久。"

#. ~ Profession (female Amateur Dog Trainer) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"As a high school student, you were the only member of a canine training "
"club.  You've always been into dogs, but you barely manage to get Fido to "
"sit.  Unfortunately, you'll need to learn quick or you and Fido aren't going"
" to last long in this new world."
msgstr "高中时期，你是犬类训练社的唯一成员。你一直很喜欢狗，但连让菲多坐下都勉强。不幸的是，你必须快速学习，否则你和菲多在这个新世界活不了多久。"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Dog Fighting Breeder"
msgstr "斗狗繁殖者"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Dog Fighting Breeder"
msgstr "斗狗繁殖者"

#. ~ Profession (male Dog Fighting Breeder) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You never cared for anything until you got caught up in a dog fighting ring."
"  You weren't really any good, but now there's no one else to be better than"
" you.  Time to train some dogs to take down the newly undead!"
msgstr "你曾对一切漠不关心，直到卷入斗狗团伙。你并不在行，但现在没人比你更强了。是时候训练一些狗来对付新出现的亡灵了！"

#. ~ Profession (female Dog Fighting Breeder) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You never cared for anything until you got caught up in a dog fighting ring."
"  You weren't really any good, but now there's no one else to be better than"
" you.  Time to train some dogs to take down the newly undead!"
msgstr "你曾对一切漠不关心，直到卷入斗狗团伙。你并不在行，但现在没人比你更强了。是时候训练一些狗来对付新出现的亡灵了！"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Professional Canine Handler"
msgstr "专业犬类驯导师"

#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Professional Canine Handler"
msgstr "专业犬类驯导师"

#. ~ Profession (male Professional Canine Handler) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You've been teaching dogs for all manner of things: movies, obedience, "
"tricks, and sometimes fighting.  With all your experience and money, you're "
"ready to take on the next step: the apocalypse!"
msgstr "你一直训练狗从事各种工作：电影表演、服从指令、技巧展示，有时还包括打斗。凭借丰富的经验和资金，你已准备好迎接下一步：末世求生！"

#. ~ Profession (female Professional Canine Handler) description
#: .\dog_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You've been teaching dogs for all manner of things: movies, obedience, "
"tricks, and sometimes fighting.  With all your experience and money, you're "
"ready to take on the next step: the apocalypse!"
msgstr "你一直训练狗从事各种工作：电影表演、服从指令、技巧展示，有时还包括打斗。凭借丰富的经验和资金，你已准备好迎接下一步：末世求生！"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Draco's Dog Mod"
msgstr "德拉科的犬类模组"

#. ~ Description for Draco's Dog Mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds dog crates with trainable dogs to animal shelters that can be trained "
"into attack dogs (stat boosts). Adds dog pet professions."
msgstr "在动物收容所添加带可训练犬只的狗笼，可将其训练为攻击犬（属性提升）。新增犬类宠物职业。"

