#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "Kevlar-lined small quadruped peto"
msgid_plural "Kevlar-lined small quadruped petos"
msgstr[0] "凯夫拉衬里小型四足宠物护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kevlar-lined small quadruped peto'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A heavy mattress-like armor of cloth, leather and thick linings of Kevlar, "
"originally used as protection in bullfighting. Nowadays usually worn by "
"canines in the service of local law enforcement, that protects from "
"shoulders to abdomen.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped "
"including a dog."
msgstr ""
"一种厚重的床垫式护甲，由布料、皮革和厚实的凯夫拉衬里制成，最初用于斗牛防护。如今通常由当地执法部门服务的犬只穿戴，保护范围从肩部到腹部。你可以将其穿在友好的小型四足动物身上，包括狗。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "biosilicified chitin small quadruped armor"
msgid_plural "biosilicified chitin small quadruped armors"
msgstr[0] "生物硅化几丁质小型四足护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'biosilicified chitin small quadruped armor'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift assembly of criniere, peytral and croupiere made from "
"biosilicified chitin fitted to a thin mesh. Can be used for protecting the "
"neck to flank of canines.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped "
"including a dog."
msgstr ""
"一套临时组装的护颈、胸甲和臀甲，由生物硅化几丁质制成，安装在薄网上。可用于保护犬只的颈部到侧腹。你可以将其穿在友好的小型四足动物身上，包括狗。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "chitin small quadruped armor"
msgid_plural "chitin small quadruped armors"
msgstr[0] "几丁质小型四足护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chitin small quadruped armor'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A makeshift assembly of criniere, peytral and croupiere made from chitin "
"fitted to a thin mesh. Can be used for protecting the neck to flank of "
"canines.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "一套临时组装的护颈、胸甲和臀甲，由几丁质制成，安装在薄网上。可用于保护犬只的颈部到侧腹。你可以将其穿在友好的小型四足动物身上，包括狗。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "chainmail small quadruped armor"
msgid_plural "chainmail small quadruped armors"
msgstr[0] "锁子甲小型四足护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chainmail small quadruped armor'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"Protecteth yon hund fram ful daemons!  You could put this on a friendly "
"small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "保护汝犬免受恶魔侵袭！你可以将其穿在友好的小型四足动物身上，包括狗。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "boiled leather small quadruped barding with caprison"
msgid_plural "boiled leather small quadruped bardings with caprison"
msgstr[0] "带马衣的煮制皮革小型四足动物马铠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled leather small quadruped barding with
#. caprison', 'str_pl': 'boiled leather small quadruped bardings with
#. caprison'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A full barding fofr small quadrupeds including dogs consisting of boiled "
"leather and cloth undercovering. This caparison is depicting a battle "
"between a monstrous dragon and regal griffin. Can be attached to a canine "
"for protection.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped including "
"a dog."
msgstr ""
"一套为包括狗在内的小型四足动物设计的全套马铠，由煮制皮革和布料衬底制成。这件马衣描绘了凶恶巨龙与威严狮鹫之间的战斗。可附着于犬类身上提供防护。你可以将其穿戴在友好的小型四足动物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "boiled leather small quadruped barding with bones"
msgid_plural "boiled leather small quadruped bardings with bones"
msgstr[0] "带骨饰的煮制皮革小型四足动物马铠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boiled leather small quadruped barding with
#. bones', 'str_pl': 'boiled leather small quadruped bardings with bones'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"Decorative bones affixed to leather small quadruped barding to invoke fear "
"in bandits and raiders and traders all!  You could put this on a friendly "
"small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "装饰性骨骼附着于皮革制小型四足动物马铠上，用以震慑强盗、掠夺者和商旅！你可以将其穿戴在友好的小型四足动物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "small quadruped rubber rainsuit"
msgid_plural "small quadruped rubber rainsuits"
msgstr[0] "小型四足动物橡胶雨衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small quadruped rubber rainsuit'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thin plastic covering adapted for small quadrupeds including dogs to "
"protect from acid rain and other caustic sources.  You could put this on a "
"friendly small quadruped including a dog."
msgstr "为包括狗在内的小型四足动物适配的轻薄塑料覆盖物，用于防护酸雨及其他腐蚀性物质。你可以将其穿戴在友好的小型四足动物（包括狗）身上。"

#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid "superalloy tactical small quadruped armor"
msgid_plural "superalloy tactical small quadruped armors"
msgstr[0] "超合金战术小型四足动物护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'superalloy tactical small quadruped armor'}
#: .\items\armor\dog_pets_dog_armor.json
msgid ""
"A thin mesh interwoven with superalloy plates and pouches for military "
"working small quadrupeds including dogs that covers from the dewlap to the "
"croup, down to the elbows.  You could put this on a friendly small quadruped"
" including a dog."
msgstr ""
"由超合金板与储物袋交织而成的轻薄网状护甲，专为包括狗在内的军用工作型小型四足动物设计，覆盖范围从颈垂到臀部，延伸至肘部。你可以将其穿戴在友好的小型四足动物（包括狗）身上。"

